messages.body:
Now wrap your app (or the relevant part of your component tree) with the `DdxProvider`:

```tsx
import { DdxProvider } from './contexts/ddx-context';

// In your root component or wherever appropriate:
<DdxProvider>
  <RuleDisplayComponent value="..." />
  {/* Other components that need ddxData */}
</DdxProvider>
```

This way, `useDdxValues` is called only once at the provider level, and all child components can access the ddxData via `useDdxContext()` without making additional calls.

